INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (1, 'HIV Panel', 'HIV antibody and antigen tests are essential for early detection and management of HIV infection. This panel uses advanced screening methods to identify both antibodies and antigens, allowing for detection even in the early stages of infection before symptoms appear. Early diagnosis is crucial for effective treatment and reducing the risk of transmission. Regular HIV testing is recommended for anyone who is sexually active or at risk. Our panel provides fast, confidential results and includes counseling resources for those who need support or have questions about their status. By staying informed and proactive, you can take control of your health and well-being.', 60.00, 24, 30, 1, 0);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (2, 'Chlamydia Panel', 'The Chlamydia PCR test is a highly sensitive and specific method for detecting Chlamydia trachomatis, one of the most common sexually transmitted infections. Many people with chlamydia do not experience symptoms, making regular screening important for early detection and treatment. Untreated chlamydia can lead to serious health complications, including infertility and pelvic inflammatory disease. This panel offers a quick and non-invasive test, with results available within 48 hours. Early diagnosis and treatment can prevent complications and reduce the spread of infection. Our healthcare team is available to provide guidance and answer any questions you may have about chlamydia and sexual health.',  50.00, 48, 45, 1, 2);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (3, 'Syphilis Panel', 'The Syphilis Panel includes both RPR and TPPA tests, providing comprehensive screening for syphilis at all stages. Syphilis is a bacterial infection that can cause serious health problems if left untreated, but it is easily curable with early detection and appropriate antibiotics. The RPR test screens for active infection, while the TPPA test confirms the diagnosis. Regular syphilis testing is recommended for sexually active individuals, especially those with multiple partners. Our panel ensures accurate results and offers follow-up support for those who test positive. Early intervention is key to preventing long-term complications and protecting your health.', 55.00, 24, 30, 1, 3);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (4, 'Gonorrhea Panel', 'Gonorrhea is a common sexually transmitted infection that often presents with mild or no symptoms, making it easy to overlook. Our Gonorrhea Panel uses PCR technology to detect Neisseria gonorrhoeae DNA quickly and accurately. Early detection is important to prevent complications such as pelvic inflammatory disease and infertility. This panel is suitable for anyone who is sexually active, especially those with new or multiple partners. Results are available within 48 hours, and our team provides support and guidance for treatment and prevention. Regular screening helps protect your health and the health of your partners.', 50.00, 48, 45, 1, 5);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (5, 'Full STI Panel', 'Our Full STI Panel offers comprehensive screening for a wide range of sexually transmitted infections, including HIV, chlamydia, gonorrhea, syphilis, and more. This panel is ideal for individuals seeking a thorough assessment of their sexual health, whether for routine checkups or after potential exposure. Early detection of STIs is crucial for effective treatment and preventing transmission. The panel includes both blood and urine tests, with results delivered confidentially. Our healthcare professionals are available to discuss your results and provide personalized recommendations for follow-up care or prevention strategies.', 100.00, 72, 60, 0, 1);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (6, 'Comprehensive STI Panel', 'The Comprehensive STI Panel covers HIV, syphilis, chlamydia, and gonorrhea tests in one convenient package. Designed for those who want a complete overview of their sexual health, this panel uses advanced diagnostic methods for accurate and timely results. Early detection and treatment of STIs can prevent serious health issues and reduce the risk of spreading infections to others. Our panel is suitable for routine screening or after potential exposure, and our team is committed to providing confidential, supportive care throughout the process.', 150.00, 48, 60, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (7, 'HPV Screening Panel', 'The HPV Screening Panel detects high-risk strains of Human Papillomavirus (HPV) and related infections that can lead to cervical and other cancers. HPV is one of the most common sexually transmitted infections, and many people are unaware they are infected. Regular screening is essential for early detection and prevention of complications. This panel uses sensitive DNA testing to identify high-risk HPV types, providing valuable information for your long-term health. Our healthcare team offers guidance on vaccination, prevention, and follow-up care as needed.', 120.00, 72, 45, 1, 3);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (8, 'Basic STD Panel', 'The Basic STD Panel includes essential tests for chlamydia and gonorrhea, two of the most common and treatable sexually transmitted infections. These infections often have no symptoms but can cause serious health problems if left untreated. Our panel uses PCR technology for fast and accurate results, making it easy to stay proactive about your sexual health. This affordable option is ideal for routine screening or after potential exposure. Our team is available to answer questions and provide support throughout the testing process.', 90.00, 48, 30, 2, 2);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (9, 'Hepatitis Panel', 'The Hepatitis Panel screens for Hepatitis B and C viruses, which can cause chronic liver disease and other serious health issues. Many people with hepatitis are unaware of their infection, making regular screening important for early detection and treatment. This panel uses advanced laboratory methods to identify both acute and chronic infections. Early diagnosis allows for timely intervention and reduces the risk of liver damage. Our healthcare professionals provide counseling and support for those who test positive, including information on treatment options and prevention.', 110.00, 72, 40, 1, 5);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (10, 'Womens Health Panel', 'The Women''s Health Panel covers common STIs and vaginal health markers, offering a comprehensive assessment tailored to women''s unique needs. This panel includes tests for infections, hormonal balance, and other factors that can affect reproductive health. Regular screening helps detect issues early, allowing for prompt treatment and improved well-being. Our panel is suitable for women of all ages, whether for routine checkups or specific concerns. Our team provides personalized care and guidance based on your results.', 130.00, 48, 50, 0, 1);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (11, 'HIV & Syphilis Duo Panel', 'The HIV & Syphilis Duo Panel combines rapid tests for both HIV and syphilis, two infections that can have serious health consequences if left untreated. Early detection is key to effective management and reducing the risk of transmission. This panel provides quick, reliable results and is ideal for routine screening or after potential exposure. Our healthcare professionals offer confidential counseling and support, ensuring you have the information and resources needed to make informed decisions about your health.', 80.00, 24, 30, 2, 0);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (12, 'STD Follow-up Panel', 'The STD Follow-up Panel is designed for individuals who have previously been diagnosed with an STI and need ongoing monitoring. This package includes tests to assess treatment effectiveness and check for reinfection or new infections. Regular follow-up is important for ensuring complete recovery and preventing complications. Our panel offers convenient scheduling and fast results, with personalized support from our healthcare team. Staying proactive with follow-up testing helps protect your health and the health of your partners.', 70.00, 24, 20, 1, 3);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (13, 'Herpes Simplex Panel', 'The Herpes Simplex Panel detects antibodies for HSV-1 and HSV-2, the viruses responsible for oral and genital herpes. Many people with herpes are unaware of their infection, as symptoms can be mild or absent. Early detection allows for better management of outbreaks and reduces the risk of transmission. This panel uses sensitive blood tests to identify both recent and past infections. Our healthcare professionals provide education and support for living with herpes, including treatment options and prevention strategies.', 95.00, 48, 35, 1, 5);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (14, 'Trichomoniasis Panel', 'The Trichomoniasis Panel screens for Trichomonas vaginalis infection, a common but often overlooked sexually transmitted infection. Trichomoniasis can cause symptoms such as itching, discharge, and discomfort, but many people have no symptoms at all. Early detection and treatment are important to prevent complications and reduce the risk of transmission. Our panel uses PCR technology for accurate results, and our team provides guidance on treatment and prevention. Regular screening is recommended for anyone who is sexually active.', 60.00, 24, 25, 1, 2);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (15, 'Comprehensive STD Panel', 'The Comprehensive STD Panel covers all major sexually transmitted diseases, including HIV, syphilis, hepatitis, and chlamydia. This all-in-one package is ideal for those seeking a thorough evaluation of their sexual health. Early detection of STDs is crucial for effective treatment and preventing long-term complications. Our panel includes a variety of tests to ensure accurate results, with confidential reporting and follow-up care. Our healthcare professionals are available to discuss your results and provide personalized recommendations for ongoing health and prevention.', 180.00, 72, 60, 0, 1);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (16, 'HPV & Cervical Cancer Panel', 'The HPV & Cervical Cancer Panel combines HPV DNA testing with a cervical cancer risk assessment, providing a comprehensive overview of your reproductive health. High-risk HPV strains are the leading cause of cervical cancer, making regular screening essential for early detection and prevention. This panel uses advanced laboratory methods to identify high-risk HPV types and assess your risk for cervical cancer. Our healthcare team offers guidance on vaccination, prevention, and follow-up care, empowering you to take control of your health.', 140.00, 72, 50, 2, 0);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (17, 'Quick STD Panel', 'The Quick STD Panel offers rapid tests for HIV, syphilis, and gonorrhea, providing fast and reliable results for those who need answers quickly. This panel is ideal for routine screening, pre-employment checks, or after potential exposure. Early detection of STDs allows for prompt treatment and reduces the risk of complications. Our panel uses advanced diagnostic methods for accuracy, and our healthcare professionals are available to discuss your results and provide support as needed.', 100.00, 24, 20, 1, 3);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (18, 'Chlamydia & Gonorrhea Panel', 'The Chlamydia & Gonorrhea Panel uses PCR tests to detect two of the most common sexually transmitted infections. Both infections can be asymptomatic but may cause serious health problems if left untreated. This panel provides fast, accurate results and is suitable for routine screening or after potential exposure. Early diagnosis and treatment help prevent complications and reduce the risk of spreading infections. Our healthcare team is available to answer questions and provide guidance on prevention and care.', 85.00, 48, 30, 1, 2);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (19, 'Syphilis & Hepatitis Panel', 'The Syphilis & Hepatitis Panel screens for syphilis and hepatitis B/C, offering a comprehensive assessment for two serious infections that can have long-term health consequences. Early detection is important for effective treatment and preventing complications such as liver disease and neurological problems. This panel uses advanced laboratory methods for accurate results, with confidential reporting and follow-up care. Our healthcare professionals provide education and support for managing these infections and reducing the risk of transmission.', 120.00, 72, 40, 0, 5);
INSERT INTO panels (id, panel_name, description, price, response_time, duration, panel_type, panel_tag) VALUES (20, 'STD Preventive Panel', 'The STD Preventive Panel is designed for routine screening and early detection of common sexually transmitted diseases. Regular testing is an important part of maintaining sexual health, especially for those with new or multiple partners. This panel includes tests for several key infections, with fast and confidential results. Our healthcare team provides personalized recommendations for prevention, vaccination, and follow-up care, helping you stay proactive about your health and well-being.', 75.00, 24, 25, 2, 0);
